Productivity Tools






Productivity Tools
Productivity tools include software and applications that enable and facilitate file sharing, collaboration, and communication. UIC students have access to Microsoft 365 and Google Workspace applications.





            Quote
          Heading link



 
Copy link




UIC students have access to Microsoft 365 and Google Workspace tools and applications that enable communication and collaboration.






            Shortcuts
          Heading link



 
Copy link












                            Microsoft 365
                    

                Microsoft 365 is a free suite of programs that includes Office applications such as Word, Excel, PowerPoint, & Teams.
            












                            Google Workspace
                    

                Google Workspace is a suite of tools used for communication and collaboration such as Docs, Sheets, and Slides.
            












